- content_for :banner do
  .jumbotron{ style: 'margin-bottom:0;border-radius: 0;' }
    .container
      %h1.center
        Looking to
        %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-cloud-download
        download data?

.content-container.lead
  %p.center
    You are about to start a simple process to gain access to terabytes of data on the NSRR.

  %p.center
    This
    %strong
      quick
    process guides you through
    %strong
      several short steps
    of the NSRR Data Access and Use Agreement and IRB review process. You can
    also save your progress, so you can "Submit your Application" when you feel
    you're ready!
  %p.center
    %br
    = link_to submissions_launch_path(dataset: params[:dataset]), method: :post, class: 'btn btn-lg btn-call-to-action' do
      Click here to start!
      %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-arrow-right

  %hr.divider-md

  %p.center
    If you need any help with this process, email us at:
    = mail_to 'support@sleepdata.org'
